title: MisterMusic Show 368 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 368 - 2 hours  [192kbps MP3 stereo]


On the show this week, new tunes from The Jungle Giants, and The Fratellis.
Plus a huge pop hit that spent 4 weeks at number one in August 1976 is the 'Oldie of the Week'.
It's a blend of over 5 decades of indie, alternative and rock.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
